      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNACCEPTABLE NIK (7) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, paving the way for a 1.2 lengths win at this track over 525m in 30.28. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. REINDEER KEITH (2) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 1.2 lengths away in second (30.37) at this track in a Mix 6/7 H over 525m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Deserves a win and gets his chance. UNCLE STILTSKIN (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 30.42 beating VICTORY YACHT. Can measure up again. MY LONG BLACK (3) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
